description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-06-2013 FRI






The Glenn Beck Radio Program - 9-6-13 








The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET, 



Buck Sexton fills in for Glenn and dives deep into Syria.
 Ex-CIA officer and National Security Analyst for the Blaze,
 Buck Sexton breaks down what is going on in Syria 
      and how it relates to the U.S. intervention. 

Also, a historic breakdown of why, when and how we even got involved in Middle East Politics.
